                        <h1><a name="57460"></a><a href="/blogs/readMore.html?id=57460">Actually back doing some work again</a></h1>
                        <div class="ItemInfo">[<a href="/blogs/selectBlog.html?id=2729&amp;articleId=57460" alt="Use this to refer to the specific blog entry">URL</a>] Posted on 4 August 2004 20:39,  <a href="/blogs/readMore.html?id=57460">0 comments in 0 threads.</a> Last comment on 4 August 2004 20:39.
                        </div>
                        <div>I have had quite a break, I had some time off - bit of a burn out but I have been spending some hours putting together some
                           material for the Shards group. The biggest problem I have is the stats for NPCs - they just take <i>way</i> too long to lay out, so I will be putting together a simple app to get people to enter them into there and then I can auto-generate
                           the layout making that whole portion of it simple and easy and <b>standard</b>. 
                           
                           The first Shard in the list is making its way much closer to release now, I would expect it out within a couple of weeks -
                           FASA willing. 
                           
                           Bye for now!
                           Richard
                        </div><br></td>
