                        <h1><a name="32752"></a><a href="/blogs/readMore.html?id=32752">*sigh* Finally back into the Earthdawn fold</a></h1>
                        <div class="ItemInfo">[<a href="/blogs/selectBlog.html?id=2729&amp;articleId=32752" alt="Use this to refer to the specific blog entry">URL</a>] Posted on 3 July 2004 18:39,  <a href="/blogs/readMore.html?id=32752">0 comments in 0 threads.</a> Last comment on 3 July 2004 18:39.
                        </div>
                        <div>It has been a hectic couple of weeks for me, my company sent me out of town and I had to stay at an apartment that had no
                           internet and work on premisis where I wasn't allowed to plug in so I have been pretty much internet-less for the last little
                           while.
                           
                           Things are starting to progress again now though, I have more artwork so I will be working with the Shards developers on starting
                           to progress a number more of those in the next week. Unfortunately, it looks like after next week I may be out again for a
                           week, but such is life!
                           
                           Enjoy your weekend those who are just starting it!
                        </div><br></td>
