                        <h1><a name="9452"></a><a href="/blogs/readMore.html?id=9452">Fixed some nasty problems in the web site</a></h1>
                        <div class="ItemInfo">[<a href="/blogs/selectBlog.html?id=2729&amp;articleId=9452" alt="Use this to refer to the specific blog entry">URL</a>] Posted on 9 June 2004 16:03,  <a href="/blogs/readMore.html?id=9452">0 comments in 0 threads.</a> Last comment on 9 June 2004 16:03.
                        </div>
                        <div>The content management system wasn't working properly and the help was disappearing for the campaigns. 
                           
                           Ok, so we have been through a few more iterations of the Shard we are all working on as well, as it turns out, James is a
                           pretty picky blighter :-) He seems to have a half-magic talent for editing!
                        </div><br></td>
