                        <h1><a name="3170"></a><a href="/blogs/readMore.html?id=3170">ok, i have ceased fiddling with the site for now</a></h1>
                        <div class="ItemInfo">[<a href="/blogs/selectBlog.html?id=2729&amp;articleId=3170" alt="Use this to refer to the specific blog entry">URL</a>] Posted on 4 June 2004 15:29,  <a href="/blogs/readMore.html?id=3170">0 comments in 0 threads.</a> Last comment on 4 June 2004 15:29.
                        </div>
                        <div>I had a number of other web sites that use the same framework that I had to iron out, as well as some little databasey issues
                           and error logging which was the biggest pain.
                           
                           I have a couple more tweaks to make to the web site in terms of syndication (I want to syndicate the rpgcampaigns and the
                           forums) and then I will be moving onto my duties in the Shards and Compact Edition areas as our artists are really coming
                           along nicely!
